{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block breadcrumbs %}{% endblock %}
{% block body %}
<div class="text-center text-secondary pt-5" {{ stimulus_controller('popover') }}>
    <h1>That all you got?</h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-4" style="max-width: 960px;">
        A legendary Flesh and Blood collection isn't built just by luck in cracking packs â€” it's crafted with strategy. <br />
This fanmade tool helps you forge your perfect collection, showing you what cards you have collected, which playsets need completion, and where your arsenal still has gaps to fill.
    </p>
    {# <p>Start by searching for cards or:</p> #}
    {# https://storage.googleapis.com/fabmaster/cardfaces/2022-UPR/UPR189.png #}

    <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="feature fixed-feature-box d-flex flex-column p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm text-center">
                    <div class="feature-top mb-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-person-circle feature-icon text-warning"></i>
                        <h4>Create an account</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-body mb-2">
                        <p>Once you have an account and are logged in you can start adding cards to your online collection.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-footer" {{ stimulus_controller('popover') }}>
                        {% if not is_granted('IS_AUTHENTICATED') %}
                            <A type="button" role="button" class="btn btn-warning" href="{{ path('app_register') }}">Sign up</a>
                        {% else %}
                            <span class="d-inline-block" tabindex="0" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-trigger="hover focus" data-bs-content="You're already signed in :)">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" disabled>Sign up</button>
                            </span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="feature fixed-feature-box d-flex flex-column p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm text-center">
                    <div class="feature-top mb-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-collection feature-icon text-warning"></i>
                        <h4>Track Your Collection</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-body mb-2">
                        <p>View all cards from a specific <a href="{{ path('app_card_setoverviewpage') }}" class="link-warning link-offset-2 link-underline-opacity-50 link-underline-opacity-100-hover">booster set</a>, dive into a <a href="{{ path('app_card_classoverviewpage') }}" class="link-warning link-offset-2 link-underline-opacity-50 link-underline-opacity-100-hover">class</a> or hunt down <a href="{{ path('app_collection_managepromocollection') }}" class="link-warning link-offset-2 link-underline-opacity-50 link-underline-opacity-100-hover">promos</a>. Your collection, organized the way you collect.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-footer"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="feature fixed-feature-box d-flex flex-column p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm text-center">
                    <div class="feature-top mb-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-file-check feature-icon text-warning"></i>
                        <h4>Complete Your Playsets</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-body mb-2">
                        <p>
                            Easily spot incomplete playsets by hiding complete sets. <br />
                            Switch between 'player view'
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle text-warning"
                               aria-label="Info"
                               tabindex="0"
                               role="button"
                               data-bs-toggle="popover"
                               data-bs-trigger="hover focus"
                               data-bs-placement="bottom"
                               data-bs-html="true"
                               title="Player view"
                               data-bs-content="<p>A playset is considered complete when you have collected three copies within the same set, regardless of the printing.</p><p>Eg.: 2 NF Sink Below (red) + 1 RF Sink Below (red) is a complete playset.</p>"
                               style="cursor: pointer;"></i>
                            and 'collector view'
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle text-warning"
                               aria-label="Info"
                               tabindex="0"
                               role="button"
                               data-bs-toggle="popover"
                               data-bs-trigger="hover focus"
                               data-bs-placement="bottom"
                               title="Collector view"
                               data-bs-html="true"
                               data-bs-content="<p>Each printing of a card is considered a separate playset.</p><p>Eg.: Sink Below (red) has 4 separate playsets in WTR: Alpha NF, Alpha RF, Unlimited NF and Unlimited RF.</p>"
                               style="cursor: pointer;"></i>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-footer"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="feature fixed-feature-box d-flex flex-column p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm text-center">
                    <div class="feature-top mb-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-p-circle-fill feature-icon text-warning"></i>
                        <h4>View All Promos</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-body mb-2">
                        <p>Stay up to date with all the promo cards, making sure you never miss a rare or limited-time offering.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-footer"></div>
                </div>
            </div> #}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .features-section {
        padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .fixed-feature-box {
        width: 340px;
        height: 300px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-top {
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .feature-body {
        flex-grow: 1;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0 5px;
    }

    .feature-body p {
        margin: 0;
    }

    .feature-footer {
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
        .fixed-feature-box {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
        }
    }
</style>




